--- CMD 7: --help ---
Usage: ruleprobe [options] [command]

Verify whether AI coding agents follow the instruction files they're given

Options:
  -V, --version                                     output the version number
  -h, --help                                        display help for command

Commands:
  parse [options] <instruction-file>                Parse an instruction file and output extracted rules
  verify [options] <instruction-file> <output-dir>  Parse rules from instruction file, verify agent output against them
  tasks                                             List available task templates
  task <template-id>                                Output the full task prompt for a given template
  compare [options] <instruction-file> <dirs...>    Run verification against multiple agent outputs and produce a comparison
  help [command]                                    display help for command

